contents.Text: [[[warning:NOTE]]] This will display a progress bar and will not be able to be stopped once started.
After the [[[strong:Downloader]]] has finished, this will call the [[[strong:Duplicate Detector]]] automatically.
[[[warning:NOTE]]] This will use the [[[strong:Select Similarity Mode]]] as the similarity mode for the [[[strong:Duplicate Detector]]] automatically.
This selects what mode you want to use for the [[[strong:Duplicate Detector]]].
[[[strong:Very Fast]]] This is the fastest but results in only the most obvious duplicates.
[[[strong:Fast]]] This is the 2nd fastest but its a little more accurate.
[[[strong:Balanced]]] This is the middle of the two and is a good balance between speed and accuracy to compute time.
[[[strong:Thorough]]] This is very accurate but results in 500K comparisons in my case with [[[strong:21000]]] songs
[[[strong:Fingerprint Only]]] This is the most accurate but takes a very long time to compute and results in [[[strong:9 million]]] comparisons with [[[strong:21000]]] songs.
